en_187446_0	A 49-year-old person had died after he was assaulted by the husband of his paramour.
en_187446_1	The incident had occurred in Dimbulapathana in Kotagala last night (Apr. 01).
en_187446_2	The suspect had attacked his wife and the victim with a mammoty.
en_187446_3	The injured were admitted to the Kotagala Hospital and the victim died at the hospital due to injuries.
en_187446_4	The suspect was arrested.
